@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #F5F5F5
skinparam ArrowColor #555555
[*] --> Completed
Completed --> Pending : approve
Pending --> Closed : cancel
Closed --> Rejected : cancel
Rejected --> Archived : submit
Rejected : entry / log message
Archived --> Approved : process
Approved --> [*]
@enduml